17:29.040 --> 17:30.960
What do you want?

17:30.960 --> 17:36.000
Two pints of lager and a bag of salt
and vinegar crisps, please, Navid.

17:36.000 --> 17:40.240
Salt and vinegar...
salt and vinegar...salt and vinegar.

17:40.240 --> 17:42.720
Isa, jump down to the cellar,

17:42.720 --> 17:45.080
get a box of salt and vinegar
crisps, will you?

17:45.080 --> 17:47.120
