17:47.120 --> 17:49.040
I work for you in the shop.

17:52.160 --> 17:54.280
A large whisky, please, Navid.

17:56.200 --> 17:58.320
Am I having a stroke?

17:58.320 --> 18:00.040
What's he...

18:00.040 --> 18:01.480
Don't ask.

18:03.440 --> 18:04.800
There you go.

18:04.800 --> 18:06.640
What's that?

18:06.640 --> 18:08.160
That's a whisky.

18:08.160 --> 18:09.840
No, I asked for a large whisky.

18:09.840 --> 18:11.400
Aye. But that'll do.

18:13.840 --> 18:16.880
Look, there's no' even enough in
there to clean my specs!

18:16.880 --> 18:19.280
Get another one in there.
No. What?

18:19.280 --> 18:22.600
I have known you for many years
and you only have two moods,

18:22.600 --> 18:24.680
despondency or rage.

18:24.680 --> 18:26.600
I believe the reason for this is

18:26.600 --> 18:28.920
that you are constantly
nursing a hangover.

18:28.920 --> 18:30.800
And that's why I want
a large whisky,

18:30.800 --> 18:32.520
because I've got a hangover.

18:32.520 --> 18:36.720
I'm trying to save you from the
endless roundabout of misery. OK.

18:38.040 --> 18:41.320
I'll be the first to admit that I do
drink a wee bit too much

18:41.320 --> 18:43.760
and I suppose I am on a bit of a
roundabo...

18:43.760 --> 18:46.240
Look, just get me a large whisky
in there,

18:46.240 --> 18:49.080
right now, before I say
something I regret!

18:49.080 --> 18:50.520
Say it.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.800
I want Boabby back.

18:59.360 --> 19:01.040
Where's my crisps?

19:01.040 --> 19:02.160
