19:17.800 --> 19:19.720
It's stone dead in here.

19:19.720 --> 19:22.960
TRANSLATION:

19:22.960 --> 19:26.200
Just take the afternoon.

19:27.720 --> 19:29.160
I've got this.

19:29.160 --> 19:31.640
SHE LAUGHS

19:38.680 --> 19:40.520
BUZZER

19:43.520 --> 19:45.160
THEY ROAR

19:45.160 --> 19:47.200
HE SCREAMS

19:52.720 --> 19:54.520
