19:54.520 --> 19:57.400
I'm Doctor Who.
We're going back in time.

19:57.400 --> 20:00.040
HE SINGS

20:00.040 --> 20:02.360
Winston, keep an eye there.

20:02.360 --> 20:05.520
Tell me when Davros is coming out
from the back shop.

20:06.840 --> 20:08.200
Psst.

20:11.360 --> 20:13.520
Bit of service here, please, Navid.

20:13.520 --> 20:16.080
Certainly, Tam. What can I get you?

20:16.080 --> 20:18.040
Uh...a cheese toastie,

20:18.040 --> 20:20.840
