Scampi Fries, please.

20:22.440 --> 20:26.040
Toastie, Cointreau, Scampi Fries.
28 pence, please.

20:33.160 --> 20:36.000
It'll be a couple of minutes
for your toastie.

20:36.000 --> 20:39.560
Oh, I don't mind waiting, Navid.
I like my cheese well melted.

20:39.560 --> 20:43.360
Sometimes, you know,
I think my brain has melted.

20:43.360 --> 20:47.040
I mean, what was I thinking,
coming round here to run a pub?

20:47.040 --> 20:50.400
I don't know the cost of anything
in a licensed public house.

20:50.400 --> 20:53.560
I'm just a daft Muslim
who runs a corner shop.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.560
BELL RINGS

20:55.560 --> 20:57.160
Oh, there's your toastie.

21:01.760 --> 21:03.600
28 pence, please.

21:05.040 --> 21:08.240
There you go. Thank you.

21:08.240 --> 21:11.400
Oh, I nearly forgot!
What do you want in your Cointreau?

21:11.400 --> 21:13.240
Just a wee dash of lemonade, please.

21:13.240 --> 21:17.600
So that's 28 pence for the drink,
the snack and the toastie

21:17.600 --> 21:19.400
and...

21:24.160 --> 21:27.120
...and £4.12 for the dash.

21:27.120 --> 21:30.240
Do you think my head buttons up
the back? Chancer!

21:41.360 --> 21:42.800
Jack! Victor!

21:44.200 --> 21:46.000
Fergie?

21:49.400 --> 21:51.280
Terrible, innit? Oh...

21:51.280 --> 21:55.560
Him sitting there, only
a year married, and look at him.

21:55.560 --> 21:56.920
Poor Sinead.

21:56.920 --> 21:59.480
I thought that boy had
his head screwed on.

21:59.480 --> 22:02.200
I don't know where
he got such an idea.

22:02.200 --> 22:04.320
Sweet sherry, Navid.

22:04.320 --> 22:05.960
(Fergie!)

22:09.520 --> 22:12.120
How yous doing?
Are yous good? Aye?

22:12.120 --> 22:14.720
"How yous doing"?!
What are YOU doing? Eh?

22:14.720 --> 22:16.880
I'm just doing
what you told me to do.

22:16.880 --> 22:19.160
What did we tell you to do?
Seize the day!

22:19.160 --> 22:20.920
I never said that!

22:20.920 --> 22:22.440
What did I say? Carpe diem.

22:22.440 --> 22:24.400
That's right. Seize the day!

22:24.400 --> 22:26.000
No, that's no' what it means.

22:26.000 --> 22:28.760
It means do the right thing,
toe the line, behave yourself.

22:28.760 --> 22:32.280
Winston, what's your understanding
of the term "carpe diem"?

22:32.280 --> 22:36.280
Seize the day. Act immediately.
Now is the moment.

22:36.280 --> 22:38.560
It means get her knickers off!

22:38.560 --> 22:40.640
Scantium pull-doonium!

22:40.640 --> 22:42.280
Panties removis!

22:42.280 --> 22:44.000
THEY GROAN

22:44.000 --> 22:45.160
Navid, two lager, please.

22:45.160 --> 22:48.400
What did you do with the two
that I gave you? We drank them!

22:48.400 --> 22:50.640
And you're wanting another
two already?

22:50.640 --> 22:53.400
Give it another half hour,
I'll consider it.

22:53.400 --> 22:55.920
Stick another goldie in there,
Navid.

22:55.920 --> 22:59.640
Not for another 12 minutes,
you red-faced inebriate bastard.

23:02.040 --> 23:04.520
Fergie, listen to me.
You're a married man.

23:04.520 --> 23:07.960
Calm down. I'm just sitting with
the lassie, having a juice.

23:07.960 --> 23:09.560
It's all very innocent.

23:09.560 --> 23:14.400
Fergie, I thought it'd be nice to
ask my parents to join us.

23:14.400 --> 23:19.320
Mum, Dad, this is Fergie,
my new boyfriend.

23:19.320 --> 23:21.520
HE GASPS

23:23.320 --> 23:25.680
Fergie, you filthy wee pig.

23:25.680 --> 23:27.200
Sinead!

23:28.440 --> 23:30.240
Carpe dum-dums.

23:35.120 --> 23:37.480
'Mugged by a couple of kids.

23:37.480 --> 23:39.120
'How embarrassing.

23:40.200 --> 23:41.680
'Still...

23:41.680 --> 23:43.280
'nobody seen it.

23:43.280 --> 23:45.160
'Nobody needs to know.'

23:59.040 --> 24:01.080
BUZZER

24:02.440 --> 24:04.040
HE CLEARS HIS THROAT

24:04.040 --> 24:05.520
Hi, Meena.

24:05.520 --> 24:07.200
TRANSLATION:

24:12.800 --> 24:15.840
Well? It's a simple question.

24:15.840 --> 24:17.760
What was the question again?

24:19.600 --> 24:23.920
I asked you who that lassie was
that came in when I kissed you.

24:25.160 --> 24:29.080
Well, that lassie that came in
there...

24:29.080 --> 24:30.600
