24:32.160 --> 24:33.640
Who was that?

24:33.640 --> 24:35.040
Jack?

24:36.440 --> 24:38.000
Eh, Victor?

24:38.000 --> 24:40.160
Winston?

24:40.160 --> 24:42.680
Tam?

24:42.680 --> 24:44.240
Eric?

24:44.240 --> 24:45.880
Navid?

24:45.880 --> 24:48.600
The lassie is Sinead, Fergie's wife.

24:48.600 --> 24:50.800
The wee creep's married.

24:52.000 --> 24:55.880
You snake! Right, you, you wee
shit!

24:55.880 --> 24:59.720
It's no' KFC you're getting the
night. It's GBH.

24:59.720 --> 25:02.360
RAISED VOICES

25:04.720 --> 25:06.240
Quiet, please.

25:06.240 --> 25:07.760
Can you be quiet?

25:07.760 --> 25:10.080
THEY TALK OVER EACH OTHER

25:10.080 --> 25:11.720
Be quiet!

25:11.720 --> 25:15.480
Thank you. Right, Isa, will you tell
us what you saw?

25:15.480 --> 25:19.560
Aye. Well, there's things I saw
but I heard much more.

25:19.560 --> 25:23.280
Mary Shaw, that works in the
laundromat... Yous know Mary?

25:23.280 --> 25:25.000
She's just left her man

25:25.000 --> 25:28.800
cos he was stealing knickers
off washing lines...

25:28.800 --> 25:30.400
Yes, I know!

25:30.400 --> 25:33.400
Anyhow, she said that
Fergie and Kayleigh

25:33.400 --> 25:36.280
have been getting right pally
these last few days.

25:36.280 --> 25:39.200
I heard that an' all. I knew you two
would be in here.

25:39.200 --> 25:42.320
I've no' done anything!
Shut up! You'll get your say.

25:42.320 --> 25:44.560
Thanks very much, Isa. Now be quiet.

25:44.560 --> 25:46.880
What do you think she means
by "pally"?

25:46.880 --> 25:49.680
Pally? I'll tell you what she
means by "pally".

25:49.680 --> 25:51.280
You doing the dirty with my man!

25:51.280 --> 25:53.600
Oh, well,
maybe if you'd paid attention to him

25:53.600 --> 25:56.040
he widnae be sniffing round me!
What?!

25:56.040 --> 25:58.960
THEY ALL SHOUT

26:01.800 --> 26:03.480
Shut up!

26:03.480 --> 26:05.440
Every one of you!

26:05.440 --> 26:09.200
Two minutes I'm down there changing
a barrel, and I come up to what?

26:09.200 --> 26:11.160
Arma-bastard-geddon!

26:11.160 --> 26:15.360
You've got 30 seconds to take this
low-order, scum-sucking,

26:15.360 --> 26:20.480
