Jeremy Kyle behaviour out of my pub!

26:20.480 --> 26:22.960
Right, you heard the man. Come on.

26:27.120 --> 26:30.080
Listen, Sinead. I didnae have any
idea he was married.

26:30.080 --> 26:34.800
Really? Really. But the main thing
is, nothing happened.

26:34.800 --> 26:36.640
Nothing at all.

26:43.000 --> 26:46.920
I'm sorry. I just wanted to see
what was out there.

26:46.920 --> 26:51.040
Fergie,
maybe we did get married too young.

26:52.520 --> 26:54.160
Go and see what's out there.

26:57.040 --> 26:58.640
Pint of lager, please.

26:58.640 --> 27:02.800
Aye, we'll take two lager
and, uh, Isa'll have a sherry.

27:02.800 --> 27:04.760
No! I'm
no' selling any more alcohol.

27:04.760 --> 27:06.160
What's your problem?

27:06.160 --> 27:09.560
You stand in that shop of yours
and you serve booze all day! Aye.

27:09.560 --> 27:12.560
But you go back to your rats'
nests and consume it.

27:12.560 --> 27:14.680
But in here, I have to witness it.

27:14.680 --> 27:17.120
It is like Sodom and Gomorrah...

27:17.120 --> 27:18.760
with crisps.

27:22.040 --> 27:23.640
You win.

27:23.640 --> 27:25.600
I want my pub back.

27:25.600 --> 27:27.760
NAVID CHUCKLES

27:27.760 --> 27:29.960
Oh, this is a great day.

27:29.960 --> 27:31.720
You want your pub back

27:31.720 --> 27:35.360
because my wee cushy number isnae
cushy at all, right?

27:36.400 --> 27:37.880
Right.

27:37.880 --> 27:39.440
Say it.

27:39.440 --> 27:40.760
Say what?

27:40.760 --> 27:43.360
"Navid, your shop is no' cushy."

27:46.400 --> 27:48.640
Your shop is no' cushy.

27:48.640 --> 27:51.600
