27:51.600 --> 27:53.720
Damn right it's not cushy!

27:53.720 --> 27:57.520
But this pub?
This pub is crazy cushy!

27:57.520 --> 27:59.680
Piece of piss!

27:59.680 --> 28:01.800
Boabby, kiss my ar...

28:01.800 --> 28:05.080
THUMPS AND GROANS

28:06.800 --> 28:09.120
Bastarding pub.

28:38.120 --> 28:40.240
He's got a lovely arse.

28:40.240 --> 28:42.120
I deserved that.

28:42.120 --> 28:44.360
Oh, love's young dream!

28:44.360 --> 28:45.960
Hey, lads.

28:45.960 --> 28:48.040
Yous two patched things up, aye?

28:48.040 --> 28:51.760
Aye, after an appropriate
amount of grovelling. Six days.

28:51.760 --> 28:53.680
Aye, and two weeks in Santa Ponsa.

28:53.680 --> 28:56.440
Oh, that's excellent. Oh,
it's good you've sorted it out, eh?

28:56.440 --> 28:57.960
Que sera, sera.

28:57.960 --> 29:00.520
